618
00:40:35.556 --> 00:40:38.726
Prve ove velike ptice
će Boing isporučiti


619
00:40:38.809 --> 00:40:41.353
Pan Americi 1969 godine.

620
00:40:43.147 --> 00:40:46.525
[LUDTKE] 747 je bio ogroman uspeh.

