646
00:42:12.653 --> 00:42:14.363
Super, super. Dobar posao momci!

647
00:42:14.446 --> 00:42:16.865
-[ZAPOSLEN 1] Evo ga, prvi.
-[ZAPOSLEN 2] Prvi.


648
00:42:18.492 --> 00:42:22.121
Volela sam da radim u Boingu jer
